GridLens
========

Carbon intensity and generation data are provided by the National Energy System
Operator (NESO) via the Carbon Intensity API (https://carbonintensity.org.uk),
used under the Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International Licence (CC BY 4.0):
https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

GridLens is an independent open-source project and is not affiliated with or
endorsed by NESO.
